ect line of your announcement, and we in the staff will lock the thread when we see it (and delete the replies if any). Only use this feature if you are making a simple and uncontroversial announcement like for example that you are recruiting certain classes. This is not a free ticket to flame people without them speaking back, or any such bullshit. <br><br>Third, we in the staff will not keep track of who represent a guild and who doesn't. If someone make a announcement or request a link change in the Guild Links section, then we will go along with it unless it's a obvious fake. If the poster doesn't represent you, then it's up to you to say so. This is also why e-mailed requests for changes to the Guild Links section gets ignored. Post your requests here instead, and we'll treat them as real, comfortable with that someone would have spoken up if it was fake. <br><br>Finally, I hope that this new section will come to good use. Happy hunting everyone! <p>Love, Edeina<br>Retired Highelf Arch Mage of Erollisi.<br>Citizen of <a href="http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero">Ayonae Ro</a>, member of <a href="http://www.eternalwrath.org">Eternal Wrath</a>.</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm14.emailToFriend?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm14.threadControl?topicID=3.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm14.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayon